<p>If you use Amazon IDU, you must not use <a href="#3150">Amazon VCS</a> because in this case, invoice documents would be uploaded to Amazon twice. This can result in missing invoices in the Seller Central due to throttling.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
