<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Send shipping confirmation first</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Note that you can only upload an invoice to Amazon after a shipping confirmation was sent to Amazon.</p>
</div>
</td>
